Vendored RNNoise worklet assets for @livekit/livekit-rnnoise-processor.

These are served self-hosted (see components/rtc/state.tsx DenoiseTrackProcessor
call site) instead of the package's jsdelivr default, because:
  - the desktop shell CSP (E2EE slice 6.2b) blocks external script/wasm origins;
  - the no-CDN policy applies everywhere else too (plan §7.1 Q8).

